{"tid":2452742,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鮭魚之亂｜全台逾300人改名 員工呻廚餘增5倍 批食客貪小便宜","createTime":"2021-03-19T04:32:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-19T05:25:13.000Z","uid":130626,"like":8,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"8b89d3c2548c565c28eea68a6d08dcdccaf9e9ce","tid":2452742,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T04:32:10.000Z","msg":"一名壽司郎員工在社交網站上傳照片，指客人只將壽司上面的魚生吃掉，留下7碗滿滿的白飯，該名員工表示，親自整理的桌子，有客人點了4、5盤魚生都沒吃，茶碗蒸原封不動，拉麵只吃上層的食材，甜品只咬一口，痛斥「真的是該下地獄轉生成100次鮭魚」。而根據同事的消息，昨天（18日）餐廳的廚餘量是平常假日的6倍。<br />\n<br />\n事主表示，今次壽司郎舉辦活動，部份員工被要求加班或者放假被要求支援，他自己也忙到頭暈想吐吃不下飯，事主認為「吃免費可以，浪費食物真的是收桌到心痛。」又指活動漏洞太多，引來一堆貪小便宜的顧客，直言「只能說高層的政策搞死人。」<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210319/VOHAMOQ3GRFZDNVXU5T2SYUI2Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210319%2FVOHAMOQ3GRFZDNVXU5T2SYUI2Y%2F&d=Ip59BN4yZo1XWf66eFhBSrnp9gp%2BSvHPFRLSSJzTNPo%3D&h=955d7978\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210319%2FVOHAMOQ3GRFZDNVXU5T2SYUI2Y%2F&h=f5669e58\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210319/VOHAMOQ3GRFZDNVXU5T2SYUI2Y/</a>"},{"pid":"8492ff3fc7f575ad661105fac97062b6bb8729aa","tid":2452742,"uid":242537,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T04:35:58.000Z","msg":"神又係你 鬼又係你"},{"pid":"576b0f9aa095f4d03d37f33e3d6edaf189f344cc","tid":2452742,"uid":20454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T05:03:38.000Z","msg":"平時食都想叫走飯<br />\n魷魚天婦羅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />壽司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8242dd70b70175c156dcc4db5d85e907ca01e3f","tid":2452742,"uid":183844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-19T05:05:28.000Z","msg":"唔通唔特登改名嘅客就唔哂咩<br />\n如果單純搞活動<br />\n你做壽司都知啲飯一定會剩<br />\n仲要任食喎<br />\n點解唔淨係出刺身"},{"pid":"00ef0d3248415917d0e26f3d76909373d6ed3213","tid":2452742,"uid":4